<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449746>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. a–b. Genitalia of Eupithecia nemrutica sp. n., (scale bar: 1 mm). a. Male genitalia, with sternite A8, holotype; b. Female genitalia, paratype." ;
